{
  "id": "adv_event_2107_01_01",
  "title": "悩める遙子",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 2.499999976158142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます\n……あれ？　少し日焼けしました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚\nHuh? Did you get a bit tanned?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7,
      "endTime": 7.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "そう見えます？\n実はイベントに出演して野外ステージで歌ったんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do I look tanned?\nActually I was singing on an outdoor stage at an event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.966666666666667,
      "endTime": 14.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと日焼け対策してんけど\n夏の日差しには敵わんかったわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I put on sunscreen and all‚\nbut the summer sunshine is just too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.266666666666667,
      "endTime": 19.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの野外ライブ……\n凄く盛り上がりそう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An outdoor TRINITYAiLE live…\nThat’d be super lively.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.833333333333332,
      "endTime": 23.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "それはもう、お客さんも沢山詰めかけて\n大盛り上がりやったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There was a large audience packed in there‚\nand it got really exciting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24,
      "endTime": 29.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "野外ステージか……\nそういえばサニピのデビューライブも野外だったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An outdoor stage…\nCome to think of it‚ Sunny Peace’s debut live was outdoors‚ wasn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9,
      "endTime": 36.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "高台の公園の野外ステージ……懐かしい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The outdoor stage in a park on a hill… so nostalgic…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6,
      "endTime": 41.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "私がバイトしてたスーパーの前で\n歌ったこともあったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also sang in front of the supermarket\nwhere I had a part-time job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.46666666666667,
      "endTime": 45.840000044382535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "あれは野外ステージと言っていいのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Does that count as an outdoor stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 49.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば遙子さんはサニピに加入する前は\nソロやったんよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ before you joined Sunny Peace‚ Haruko-san‚\nyou were solo‚ weren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50,
      "endTime": 55.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "その頃は野外ライブとかしてたん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you do any outdoor shows back then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.36666666666667,
      "endTime": 58.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええ、そうね……\n一人で野外イベントに出演したこともあるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Er‚ yeah…\nI have appeared on my own at an outdoor event…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.43333333333333,
      "endTime": 64.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "知らなかった\nどんな様子だったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t know that.\nHow was it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 68.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まあ、昔のことはいいじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ enough old stories.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.83333333333333,
      "endTime": 71.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "ええやんか\nうちも遙子さんの武勇伝、聞きたいわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ come on.\nI want to hear your saga‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 76.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "武勇伝だなんて、そんなたいした話じゃないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not a “saga” or anything so impressive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.86666666666666,
      "endTime": 81,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4333.333333333343
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4333.333333333343
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、大変だよ！　大ニュースだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All of you listen‚ this is big news!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.2,
      "endTime": 85.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなにあわててどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you so excited?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5,
      "endTime": 87.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "それが大変なんだよ！\nさっき{user}さんから聞いたんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because this is big news!\nI heard it from {user}-san earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 93.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄で行われる夏のライブイベントに\nサニピの出演が決まったんだって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace is booked to perform at the\nsummer live event in Okinawa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 99.39999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okinawa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.63333333333334,
      "endTime": 101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "イベントではビーチに特設ステージを作って\n野外ライブをするらしいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They are building a special stage for the event‚\nfor an outdoor live show right on the beach!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2,
      "endTime": 106.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "しかもサニピの夏の新曲をそこで初披露するって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And we’ll be debuting the new Sunny Peace summer song there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 111.7333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "夏の沖縄……ビーチで野外ライブ……新曲披露……\n盛り上がること……間違いなし……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okinawa in summer… outdoor show on the beach… new song debut…\nThat’s sure to be a wild show!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.93333333333334,
      "endTime": 120.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事が終わったら\nみんなで観光とか出来たらいいな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once the work is done‚\nit’d be great if we could all do some sightseeing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 124.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "出来るんちゃう？　沖縄やし、泊まりやと思うよ\nせっかくなんやし、いろいろ楽しんだ方がええで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You probably could. It’s Okinawa‚ and you’ll likely be staying there.\nIt’d be a waste not to‚ and you could have all kinds of fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.9,
      "endTime": 133.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "観光スポットって何があったかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What tourism attractions are there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.36666666666667,
      "endTime": 136.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "有名なのは国際通りとか……水族館とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The famous things are Kokusai Street and the aquarium…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.8,
      "endTime": 141.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
